This local Debian package adapts Codex++ for the Codex Desktop Linux package
layout used by Ubuntu installs:

  /usr/bin/codex-desktop
  /opt/codex-desktop/start.sh

The package injects /usr/bin/codex-desktop by replacing it with a symlink to
/usr/bin/codex-plus-plus, while keeping a backup at:

  /usr/lib/codex-plus-plus/upstream/codex-desktop

Useful commands:

  sudo codex-plus-plus status
  sudo codex-plus-plus disable
  sudo codex-plus-plus enable
